# Root build context is used by apps/control-plane/Dockerfile (the box image
# builds from apps/cli/runtime/docker, a different context, so this file does
# not affect it). Keep host-built artifacts out of the image: the Dockerfile
# runs `pnpm install` + `turbo build` to populate node_modules/dist for the
# TARGET platform — copying the host's (wrong-arch) node_modules in breaks
# native deps like rollup's platform binary.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
.git
**/*.log
